      <title>Ardian 表示将参与 Altice 价值 70 亿欧元的 XpFibre 部门的竞标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/ardian-said-to-join-bidding-for-altice-s-7-billion-xpfibre-unit</link>
